LAHORE, Aug 11 (APP): Punjab Chief Minister Sardar Usman Buzdar has expressed a deep sense of sorrow over the death of the mother of his cameraman Abdul Salam.
In a condolence message here on Tuesday, he extended sympathies to the bereaved family and prayed to Almighty Allah to rest the departed soul in eternal peace.
